{"type":"message","id":"e8e38360","parentId":"bd563fae","timestamp":"2026-04-28T13:30:01.434Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:93b9902c-05da-42f4-bc9d-0020a2f61ebb Daily AI Briefing] You are my daily life assistant. Every morning, generate a concise and practical daily briefing for me as a husband, father, and coach. Keep it under 250 words. Format it exactly with these sections:\n\nGOOD MORNING  \nBIBLE  \nWEATHER  \nTODAY'S PRIORITY  \nFAMILY FOCUS  \nCOACHING FOCUS  \nSTOIC PRINCIPLE  \nPERSONAL DISCIPLINE  \nTONIGHT'S QUESTION  \n\nInstructions:\n- BIBLE: Include a short verse and a simple real-life application.\n- WEATHER: Briefly summarize today's weather and anything important (rain, heat, etc.).\n- STOIC PRINCIPLE: Include one Stoic idea (discipline, control, perspective) and how to apply it today.\n- TODAY'S PRIORITY: One clear focus for the day.\n- FAMILY FOCUS: One intentional action to take with my kids or wife.\n- COACHING FOCUS: One coaching emphasis (discipline, effort, leadership).\n- PERSONAL DISCIPLINE: One standard I must hold myself to today.\n- TONIGHT'S QUESTION: One strong reflection question.\n\nTone: grounded, focused, masculine, and practical. Avoid generic motivation. Make it feel like a real daily operating brief.\nCurrent time: Tuesday, April 28th, 2026 - 6:30 AM (America/Los_Angeles) / 2026-04-28 13:30 UTC\n\nUse the message tool if you need to notify the user directly for the current chat. If you do not send directly, your final plain-text reply will be delivered automatically."}],"timestamp":1777383001432}}
